        <item>
            <title>【评测】CCSToys 真三一斩星斧版　新设计头部 + 斩星斧够霸气</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/ccstoysgetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ccstoysgetter</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/ccstoysgetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 03:00:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Figure]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[超合金]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[高达]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231518</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>CCSToys 的出品一向也保持高质，但今次的真三一同一模具但出第三次的版本，真三一斩星斧版 (Getter One Stars Slasher Ver)，(前两次是初版及限定黑版)，今次的版本又表现如何呢？</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231760" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8993-694x499.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="499" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8993-694x499.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8993.jpg 1251w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲包装盒明显比旧版扇了，但也是很大盒</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231761" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8999-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8999-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8999.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲真三一斩星斧版的彩绘</p><h2>开箱：灯效及底座确定保留</h2><p>其实今次的真三一斩星斧版是提早推出了，之前本身是预计 5 月才推出的，之前预告推出时，见到售价下调了，见到网上有玩家提出疑问，除了武器量减少外，会否连灯效及底座都会被削减了？小编收到后当然立即开箱看看这两方面，可以确定灯效及底座都有保留到，玩家们不用担心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231762" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9003-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9003-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲是有底座的，不用担心</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9005-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9005-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲灯效全也保留的</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9007-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9007-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三对造型手掌，及一对可动手掌</p><h2>斩星斧版改进地方</h2><p>今次最大特色就是其金属红色的配色，所有装甲部位都改用有光泽的涂装，更配合到真三一的感觉，更长更有型的新翼，不仅在大小和造型上有所增强，其可动性和可玩性也得到了提升，这一改进让飞翼能够模拟动画中的高速飞行模式。新头部的造型更有动画设定感，眼珠更大更精灵了，线条也改了，以及加入更多透明绿色部份，胸甲部份的蓝色位置也改为透明绿色，内部则以银色制作，就算不著灯时，层次及机械感觉更加强烈，当然著灯后的灯效也更为突出。可说整只新版外观，绝对比旧版更加有型靓仔。</p><p><a title="_DSC9046" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53681456693/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53681456693_8d0ba46070_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9046" width="657" height="1024" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲金属红色的配色，所有装甲部位都改用有光泽的涂装</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231769" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9050-1-643x580.jpg" alt="" width="643" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9050-1-643x580.jpg 643w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9050-1.jpg 997w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 643px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更长更有型的新翼</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9024-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9024-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9024.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9025-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9025-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9025.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新头部的造型更有动画设定感，眼珠更大更精灵了</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9026-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9026-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9026.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲胸甲部份的蓝色位置也改为透明绿色，内部则以银色制作</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9027-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9027-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9027.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9039-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9039-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9039.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲就算不著灯时，层次及机械感觉更加强烈</p><p><a title="_DSC9193" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53681687520/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53681687520_ed4ea391b7_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9193" width="749" height="1024" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲著灯后的灯效也更为突出</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9017-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9017-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9017.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9194-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9194-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9194.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9196-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9196-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9196.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9197-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9197-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9197.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC9096" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53680369872/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53680369872_7a4d55e0db_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9096" width="1024" height="721" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可模拟动画中的高速飞行模式</p><p>虽然真三一斩星斧版在武器方面只提供一把特制的大斧，与初版和黑色版的多样武器相比略显单薄。然而，这把斩星斧可以改变刀刃的摆放方式，亦可以变换成镰刀状，全展开时非常大把亦很够霸气。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9054-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9054-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9054.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9059-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9059-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9059.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新的斩星斧非常巨大</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9055-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9055-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9055.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可拉开作镰刀状态</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9056-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9056-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9056.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9057-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9057-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9057.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不同的掌型都是为配合斩星斧握法而设</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9058-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9058-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9058.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9062-567x580.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9062-567x580.jpg 567w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9062.jpg 880w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 567px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲附设的地台</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/bandai-g-frame/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Bandai 食玩乐园登陆葵芳     G-FRAME FA 风灵彩透 + MJ GUNDAM SP 版</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/05/gundam-factory-yokohama-5/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">横滨可动高达 3 月底结束展出，闭幕礼富野由悠季 + 无人机 + 烟花</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC9069" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53681595319/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53681595319_c017523133_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9069" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9074" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53680369947/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53680369947_b82a261b51_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9074" width="1024" height="595" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9078" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53681227691/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53681227691_66a9fc5567_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9078" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9093" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53680369942/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53680369942_558ba60631_b.j