        <item>
            <title>传纸餐具易生虫，环保餐具供应商：「建议用密实袋储存」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/26/environmentally-friendly-tableware/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=environmentally-friendly-tableware</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/26/environmentally-friendly-tableware/life-tech/green-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 13:30:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[环保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[纸餐具]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[走塑]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231673</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">首阶段「走塑」周一（22 日）起实施，网上传言纸餐具易孳生昆虫，昨日（25 日）出席环保署「绿色餐具平台」示范的环保餐具供应商负责人叶柏麟相信，是因运输期间或储存不当所致，更指开封纸餐具后要妥善保管。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1231674 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240426at-1-694x429.png" alt="" width="694" height="429" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240426at-1-694x429.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240426at-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网上传言纸餐具易孳生昆虫，环保餐具供应商负责人叶柏麟相信是因运输期间或储存不当所致</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">环保餐具供应商创办人叶柏麟今日（26 日）在电台节目表示，纸餐具耐用性是受材料及设计影响，饮食业界需要自行选择合适餐具，环保餐具出厂时已涂上水性涂职及有国际应证，并不会出现食品安全问题。纸餐具在制作过程中，经历高温压制机器去到约 220 度左右，理论上不会有昆虫出现。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">叶柏麟认为，纸餐具有可能在运输或者储存过程出现问题，例如运输过程弄湿，或放在潮湿的位置。他建议用可以开关的密实袋储存延长保质期。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=558465">Now</a>、<a href="https://gbcode.rthk.hk/TuniS/news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1749809-20240421.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/bamboo-knife-cut-steak-broke-twice/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【走塑】供应商示范竹刀叉锯扒但两度截断，负责人：市民需时间适应</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/john-lee-said-no-plastic-doesnot-affect-citizen/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">李家超：「走塑」对市民影响不大，谢展寰：如替代餐具不耐用可试其他产品</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/22/paper-straw-pfas/life-tech/health/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">比利时大学：「走塑」纸饮管也可致癌 + 不育，研究指有不可降解 PFAS</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/26/environmentally-friendly-tableware/life-tech/green-2/">传纸餐具易生虫，环保餐具供应商：「建议用密实袋储存」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
